{"tid":667084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平讚香港擁眾多「愛國愛港」科技人才　愛因斯坦曾稱愛國為胡言亂語","createTime":"2018-05-16T12:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T04:54:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d49e88c5fc8af582c79cc443cf68901164eb9276","tid":667084,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"中國國家主席習近平昨日突然表示，香港擁有眾多「愛國愛港」的高質素科技人才，支持香港成為國際創科中心，是實行「一國兩制」應有之義。新華社報道指，相關部門將支持「愛國愛港」科研人員深入參與國家發展計劃，加強香港和中國的科技合作。<br />\n<br />\n不過曾因納粹黨而移民美國的著名科學家愛因斯坦，對愛國卻有非常不同的看法。他曾指「應該立即拋棄這種對文明的恥辱，聽命於人的英雄主義、不智的暴力，及所有以愛國主義為名、令人生厭的胡言亂語。（This disgrace to civilization should be done away with at once. Heroism on command, senseless violence and all the loathsome nonsense that goes by the name of patriotism）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/249823/習近平讚香港擁眾多「愛國愛港」科技人才%E3%80%80愛因/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F249823%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%AE%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%93%81%E7%9C%BE%E5%A4%9A%E3%80%8C%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E6%84%9B%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8D%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%25E3%2580%2580%E6%84%9B%E5%9B%A0%2F&d=qOvJIoHipGfKSpPHgSLS3ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=912681a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/249823/習近平讚香港擁眾多「愛國愛港」科技人才%E3%80%80愛因/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b34c559f08387fe3f5a5219757962514750ebb","tid":667084,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0cd2088212abed534a0f37d2ebf84fa86d9b46","tid":667084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"習大大面前，愛恩斯坦算什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c26afe1f79fb0d6d7704ded4c10a58890caf469","tid":667084,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201